        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-e78c72c7-6097-4e17-b155-07a50a995109">
                The Prime Minister (Mr. Churchill)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-e78c72c7-6097-4e17-b155-07a50a995109" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
